update such information as required.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activities conducted through your account. Ticpin shall not be liable for any loss arising from unauthorized use of your account.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"By registering, you consent to receive communications from Ticpin via email, SMS, push notifications, or other digital means, including transactional, service-related, and promotional messages. You may manage communication preferences through available opt-out mechanisms.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"During your use of the Platform, we may collect personal and usage data such as your name, contact details, location, device information, preferences, and booking behavior, in accordance with our Privacy Policy.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"By providing your mobile number, you expressly consent to receive calls and messages from Ticpin or its authorized service providers for purposes including customer support, service updates, and confirmations.\"}]]}]]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Use of Services\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"You agree to use the Platform and Services:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Only for lawful purposes;\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"In compliance with these Terms and applicable laws;\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Without infringing the rights of any third party;\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Without interfering with the security, functionality, or integrity of the Platform.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Any misuse of the Platform may result in suspension or termination of your access.\"}]]}]]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6 pt-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Content\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black font-bold\",\"children\":\"Definition of Content\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"“Content” includes, without limitation, text, images, photographs, videos, audio clips, reviews, ratings, messages, listings, data, and other information displayed or transmitted on the Platform.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"“Your Content” or “Customer Content” refers to any content you upload, submit, share, or display on the Platform.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"“Our Content” refers to all content created or owned by Ticpin, including software, design, interfaces, logos, trademarks, analytics, and platform features.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"“Third Party Content” refers to content provided by Organizers, Merchants, advertisers, or other third parties.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black font-bold\",\"children\":\"Content Moderation\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin reserves the right, but not the obligation, to review, remove, disable, or restrict access to any content that violates these Terms or is deemed unlawful, misleading, offensive, or inappropriate.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We are not responsible for the accuracy, legality, or reliability of Customer Content or Third Party Content.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-bl